Privacy Policy for LæringsFokus

Last updated: 2026

LæringsFokus is developed and operated by TGN.

Your privacy is important to us. This Privacy Policy explains how the app handles information.

⸻

1. Data Collection

LæringsFokus does not collect personal information such as:
	•	Name
	•	Email address
	•	Phone number
	•	Location data
	•	Contacts
	•	Photos

The app does not create user accounts.

⸻

2. Purchases

The app uses Apple’s in-app purchase system to sell credits.

All payments are handled securely by Apple.
We do not store or have access to your payment information.

⸻

3. Local Data

Some information is stored locally on your device, including:
	•	Purchased themes
	•	Credit balance
	•	Quiz progress
	•	Downloaded quiz content (for offline use)

This data stays on your device unless you delete the app.

⸻

4. Analytics & Tracking

LæringsFokus does not use third-party analytics, advertising networks, or tracking technologies.

The app does not track users across apps or websites.

⸻

5. Children’s Privacy

LæringsFokus is intended for educational use.

The app does not knowingly collect personal data from children.

⸻

6. Data Security

All purchases are processed through Apple’s secure systems.
Local data is stored using standard iOS security mechanisms.

⸻

7. Changes to This Policy

We may update this Privacy Policy if required.
Any changes will be reflected on this page.

⸻

8. Contact

If you have questions regarding this Privacy Policy, please contact:

tordgladnordahl@atea.no
